@startuml
title Where caaa sits: acceptor to acquirer
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #FBF0E4
  BorderColor #C77D2E
}
skinparam ArrowColor #C77D2E
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FBF0E4
skinparam noteBorderColor #C77D2E

actor Cardholder as CH
[POI / acceptor\n(merchant terminal)] as POI
[Acquirer] as ACQ
[Issuer] as ISS

CH --> POI : presents card
POI --> ACQ : caaa authorisation / completion
ACQ --> ISS : cain to the issuer
note bottom of POI : caaa is the acceptor-to-acquirer leg;\ncasp drives the POI from the till
@enduml
